WEBVTT

00:01:28.723 --> 00:01:32.891
My father, a mechanic by profession,

00:01:32.915 --> 00:01:35.680
worked very hard to send me to school.

00:01:37.320 --> 00:01:39.909
Just like other young people,

00:01:40.995 --> 00:01:43.288
I had a lot of plans and dreams.

00:01:44.756 --> 00:01:46.870
I wanted to complete my studies,

00:01:47.616 --> 00:01:48.948
get a nice job,

00:01:49.554 --> 00:01:52.331
marry and have my own children

00:01:52.355 --> 00:01:53.822
and support my family.

00:01:55.124 --> 00:01:57.434
But this didn't happen.

00:01:59.871 --> 00:02:06.522
War in my homeland forced me
to flee to Uganda in 2008,